Content Hierarchies!

Build Environment:
Developed with Ubuntu 14.04
Requires PHP5, Apache and Mysql
MySql root password must be "switch" or edit /db/db.inc

DB Setup:
To setup the DB execute /db/setup.sh  then setup a test

Test 1: A simple test with two hierarchies
Test 2: Includes Test 1 and a content hierarchy with more levels
Test 3: Includes Test 2 and a content hierarchy with a reference to another hierarchy
Test 4: Includes Test 3 and a content hierarchy with a recursive node

To setup a test run the .sh file e.g.

/db/test1.sh

Paul Skinner
